OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781449872
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to 'launching frying
OL,4,Cpan at police' during Nowak protest
OL,6,FA 36-year-old man has pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto violent disorder by throwing a
OL,8,Ffrying pan at police after violence
OL,9,Fbroke out in Southampton during a
OL,10,Fprotest following the murder of
OL,11,Fstudent Henry Nowak.
OL,13,FRyan Atkinson, of Highcliff Avenue,
OL,14,FSouthampton, who is the 22nd person to
OL,15,Fbe charged following the protests,
OL,16,Fentered his plea at Southampton
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
