PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781449872
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to 'launching frying
OL,4,Cpan at police' during Nowak protest
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Henry Gordon told the
OL,7,Fcourt that Atkinson had "picked up a
OL,8,Flarge frying pan and launched it at
OL,9,Fpolice" during the disorder.
OL,11,FHe remanded the defendant in custody
OL,12,Fto be sentenced at Southampton Crown
OL,13,FCourt on June 29 and told him: "I find
OL,14,Fthere are substantial grounds that if
OL,15,FI granted you bail you would commit
OL,16,Ffurther offences."
