CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781449872
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to 'launching frying
OL,4,Cpan at police' during Nowak protest
OL,6,FSo far 10 people have been jailed
OL,7,Ffollowing the demonstration involving
OL,8,F1,000 people which started outside
OL,9,FSouthampton Central Police Station on
OL,10,FJune 2 before hundreds moved on to the
OL,11,FPortswood area where Mr Nowak was
OL,12,Fkilled and where the violence started.
OL,14,FAnger had erupted after police body-
OL,15,Fworn video was released showing Mr
OL,16,FNowak being placed in handcuffs
OL,17,Fmoments before he became unconscious
OL,18,Fand subsequently died.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
