FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781449872
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to 'launching frying
OL,4,Cpan at police' during Nowak protest
OL,6,FVickrum Digwa, 23, who lived in a
OL,7,Fnearby road with his family, was
OL,8,Fjailed for life to serve a minimum of
OL,9,F21 years for his murder.
OL,11,FThe court hearings have been told that
OL,12,F13 police officers and a police dog
OL,13,Fwere injured in the protest and a
OL,14,Fmember of the public suffered a broken
OL,15,Fjaw.
OL,17,FThe police operation involved 100
OL,18,Fofficers from nine different areas
OL,19,Fwith a cost of #443,000 and a clean-up
OL,20,Fcost to the local council of #7,000,
OL,21,Fthe court heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
